Package users Description

The package that contains the classes that have to do with users, user information, and keeping records on users so that they can be impersonated by the computer. This package contains the class UserProfile, which keeps information about the user to allow the computer to predict the behavior of other users with similar information. This package also contains the class UserGameHistory, which keeps track of how well the user has done in past games, UserBehavior, which keeps track of the users behavior, and userActionLog which keeps track of every action of the user in the game so that the computer may impersonate the user, and so that the computer can predict what the user will find funny. We should look into different options for storing user data - XML or text seem the best right now
